reviewText: love this series, especially Joe Cunningham with the Gee's Bend quilters
I'm a real fan of this series.  Very informative of the very wide variety of craft being practiced in this country today.  Will continue to order the series.
A wonderful addition to my collection of Craft in America. I really enjoy this series. It is inspirational.
This is another wonderful episode of Craft in America, showing how craft and industry have merged to create in new ways.
